<%- include ("../partials/header") %>
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/index/wishlist.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sacramento&family=Hind+Vadodara&family=Anton&family=Open+Sans+Condensed:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<div class="container">
    <div class="jumbotron" id="jumbo">
        <div class="inner">
            <h1 style="color:#f5d9d5;font-family: 'Just Another Hand', cursive;font-size: 5rem;" data-aos="zoom-out">
                <%= username %>'s WishList </h1>
            <p style="color:#FEFEDF;font-family: 'Sacramento', cursive;font-size: 2rem;">because there's so much left to do...</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div id="info">
    <p>Everything we almost did but didn't. Everything we wish we could do. <br>
        We dream like we're reaching for the stars. Our bucket list overflowing.<br> So many memories waiting
        to be made and so many stories waiting to be told. <br>A whole lifetime ahead of us. I hope we never
        run out of things to do. <br>
        But someday, <br>
        When we're old and gray, <br>
        We'll cross off the last thing on our list <br>
        And talk about all the things we missed.
    </p>
</div>
<br>
<hr style="width: 70%;">
<br>
<div id="wishlist">
    <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
                <img src="https://i.imgur.com/cKqEg7B.png"
                    alt="Bucket List">
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
                <h1>MOVIES TO WATCH</h1>   
                <div>A list of movies to watch or stream.<br> <br>
                <a href="/wishlist/movies"><button class="btn btn-outline btn-dark" id="buttons">Explore!</button></a>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
                <img src="https://i.imgur.com/iKazBOP.png"
                    alt="Bucket List">
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
                <h1>PLACES TO VISIT</h1>
                <div>A list of places to visit before I die.<br> <br>
                 <a href="/wishlist/places" ><button class="btn btn-outline btn-dark" id="buttons">Explore!</button></a>
                 </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
                <img src="https://i.imgur.com/B0LlEvb.png"
                    alt="Bucket List">
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
                <h1>THINGS TO DO</h1>
                <div>A list of adventures and bucketlist wishes. <br> <br>
                      <a href="/wishlist/bucketlist"><button class="btn btn-outline btn-dark"
                              id="buttons">Explore!</button></a>
                    </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-inner">
            <div class="flip-card-front">
                <img src="https://i.imgur.com/RYYs0YZ.png"
                    alt="Avatar">
            </div>
            <div class="flip-card-back">
                <h1>OTHER STUFF</h1>
                <div>Anything I want to remember XD <br> <br>
                 <a href="/wishlist/todo"><button class="btn btn-outline btn-dark"
                         id="buttons">Explore!</button></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

